        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.traveling_merchant.desc", "The flamboyantly-dressed Traveling Merchant travels far and wide to bring unique, cultural wares from time to time.");
//        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.skeleton_merchant.desc", "Most skeletons are out for blood, but not the Skeleton Merchant. He just wants to sell supplies, such as rare torches and yo-yo gear.");
        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.old_man.desc", "This hapless Old Man carries the burden of a heavy curse. It's said at night he transforms into a horrific demon which guards the Dungeon.");
//        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.mystic_frog.desc", "A curious frog with a funny hat, surrounded by potent magic! Perhaps something can break its curse... you probably shouldn't kiss it!");
        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.bunny.desc", "Fuzzy wuzzy creatures that prefer safe, friendly locations.");
//        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.bunny_with_a_hat.desc", "Someone put a party hat on a bunny. It must be a real party animal.");
        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.explosive_bunny.desc", "Not the typical garden-variety bunny. This one has been tampered with, and has an explosive temper as a result.");
//        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.bunny_slime.desc", "Is it a bunny in a slime costume? Or is it a slime in a bunny costume? Halloween can be very confusing sometimes.");
//        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.bunny_xmas.desc", "Judging by the outfit, Santa appears to have recruited some bunnies to be his little helpers this year.");
        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.jewel_bunny.4.desc", "Rarely, critters are found coated entirely in gold! Shopkeepers will pay handsomely for these, or you can show them off in cages!");
        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.bird.desc", "A simple white bird which enjoys a calm sunny day.");
        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.blue_jay.desc", "This little blue bird came looking for worms.");
        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.cardinal.desc", "A rare, red-crested friend of the forest.");
//        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.scarlet_macaw.desc", "A lovely tropical bird with plumage that reminds one of a beautiful sunset over the jungle canopy.");
//        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.blue_macaw.desc", "Evoking visions of a bright summer sky over crystal blue waters, this tropical bird can be found foraging for seeds in the trees of the jungle.");
//        add("bestiary.entity.terra_entity.toucan.desc", "You can often find this brightly-plumed and large-beaked bird looping around high in the trees in search of delicious fruit.");
